---
// About / Nosotros Component - Fisiodermy
---

<section class="about" id="nosotros">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-image animate-on-scroll">
        <img src="/images/img-profesional.png" alt="Profesional Fisiodermy" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="about-badge">
          <span class="badge-number">+5</span>
          <span class="badge-text">Años de<br>Experiencia</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="about-content animate-on-scroll">
        <p class="section-label">Nosotros</p>
        <h2 class="about-title">Pasión por el <em>bienestar</em> y la <em>belleza</em></h2>
        <p class="about-text">
          En Fisiodermy nos dedicamos a realzar tu belleza natural y promover tu bienestar integral. Somos un centro especializado en estética avanzada y fisioterapia dermatofuncional, con un equipo de profesionales comprometidos con tu cuidado.
        </p>
        <p class="about-text">
          Utilizamos tecnología de vanguardia y productos de las mejores marcas internacionales para garantizar resultados excepcionales en cada tratamiento.
        </p>
        
        <div class="about-stats">
          <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="stat-number">+500</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Pacientes Felices</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="stat-number">+1000</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Tratamientos</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <span class="stat-number">5.0</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Rating Google</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <a href="#contacto" class="btn btn-gold">Conocer Más</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 150px 0;
    background: var(--black);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    width: 50%;
    height: 100%;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 100% 50%, rgba(201, 162, 39, 0.1) 0%, transparent 60%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 100px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-image {
    position: relative;
  }

  .about-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 650px;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center top;
  }

  .about-badge {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 40px;
    right: -40px;
    background: var(--gold);
    padding: 30px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .badge-number {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--black);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .badge-text {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--black);
    margin-top: 5px;
  }

  .about-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .about-title {
    font-size: 48px;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .about-title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .about-text {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    line-height: 2;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .about-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 50px;
    margin: 50px 0;
    padding: 40px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .stat-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 42px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--gold);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 20px 45px;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.4s ease;
  }

  .btn-gold {
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--black);
  }

  .btn-gold:hover {
    background: var(--gold-light);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(201, 162, 39, 0.4);
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 60px;
    }

    .about-badge {
      right: 20px;
      bottom: 20px;
    }

    .about-image img {
      height: 500px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-title {
      font-size: 36px;
    }

    .about-stats {
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 30px;
    }

    .stat-item {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 100px;
    }

    .stat-number {
      font-size: 32px;
    }

    .about-image img {
      height: 400px;
    }

    .about-badge {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .badge-number {
      font-size: 36px;
    }
  }
</style>